{"type": "article", "id": 31523, "title": "快开学了，我们准备了一份文具收纳指南｜这个设计了不起", "description": "每个周末，《好奇心日报》都会找个主题为你寻找精彩设计。", "date": "2016-08-26T23:24:23Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 2575, "name": "文具"}, {"id": 12527, "name": "收纳"}, {"id": 32061, "name": "TripleLiving"}, {"id": 15806, "name": "JanSport"}, {"id": 32062, "name": "一九八四"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 12, "praise_count": 753, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160826214026laSb2qFMei7rtQYx.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><p>          </p><p>          </p><p>马上就是开学季了，装备都打点好了吗？除了纸笔这样的基本文具之外，各类小包小袋和桌上收纳工具也不必可少。这个周末我们整理了一些与收纳相关的小物，除了便利的功能之外，它们的外观也十分讨巧。</p><h3>序 by 一九八四</h3><p>手机、笔记本、充电宝……相信它们都是你书桌上的常客，由此产生的一个典型的生活疑问很有可能就是“线头在哪里”。想要一张整洁有序的书桌，你可能需要来自收线器的帮助。这个名为“序”的固线器由一九八四设计，底座由两种天然木料打造而成，组装时并不需要使用额外的工具，只要将牛皮对折后插入木槽再用黄铜棒将它们固定住即可。牛皮形成的圆筒富有弹性，相邻的空间里刚好可以用来收纳五根线缆。这是它的<a href=\"https://item.taobao.com/item.htm?id=524510667254\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 49 元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160826214239E9HsWdyNl41KGS0f.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562857\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160826214237UEH4JviBMAmKftaq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160826214237QzouWL30V6R1OCim.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160826214237dlJ46CFNZWojq3we.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608262142330qiG6htfsnzVk9P8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562857\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Digital Burrito Pouch by JanSport</h3><p>如果你不喜欢每次都得从一堆乱七八糟的东西里找笔的感觉，一个设计灵活而且分区的笔袋会是一个不错的选择。老牌背包品牌 JanSport 就推出了一款名为 Digital Burrito Pouch 的卷式口袋，其中春卷款和墨西哥卷款几乎可以以假乱真，只不过里面的馅料是各种文具和数据线。如果担心自己会忍不住饿肚子的话，它还有两种以图案为主的款式，这是它的<a href=\"http://www.jansport.com/shop/en/jansport-us/digital-burrito-pouch-t69f\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 18 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160826214201swx2WknpdPoMtZ4S.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.228682\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160826214204WpZKulMJR203A4I5.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.228682\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608262142029tesdxmzUqA5jpRE.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.228682\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608262142031wIXMludCWSonj9D.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.228682\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160826214202VbUL8n3XcAg6ZY5p.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.228682\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160826214204UdH3KamJ8ue5zGpW.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.228682\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Tiny City by TripleLiving</h3><p>如果文具有自己的城市，或许就是文具组合 <a href=\"http://www.triplelivings.com/#!tinycity/mainPage\" rel=\"nofollow\">Tiny City</a> 的样子。来自台湾工作室 <a href=\"http://www.triplelivings.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">TripleLiving</a> 的设计师们将硅胶和水泥混合在一起，利用这种独特的“软水泥”打造出了“建筑物”的外墙，同时还在其中穿插了木头的元素，淡化了混凝土的冰冷，带给人一种温柔的感觉。Tiny City 中最大的那幢房子是一个笔筒，阁楼里藏着一个卷笔刀，把配套的笔套放在阁楼上就像是一个小烟囱，看起来格外有趣。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160826214104oSXEbcrMBHzR7GNy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.575000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160826214105mzagLZRvNDIUTwJ4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160826214106y56SJfv8pFOVcDGK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160826214106bnq6adfm1GKHAJtX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160826214106oZnz6eQOwArvbkFj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.728333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160826214107i5K69Y2XoxOzAEfg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>          </p><h3>Tsumugi by Ideaco</h3><p>来自大阪的设计工作室 Ideaco 的这组木质收纳简洁而实用。主体是可放水杯和手机的一块“木板”，帮助归类的同时保持清爽的视觉感受。另有一组专门放名片的小盒子，相互叠加起来就像是一个迷你的抽屉柜，也可以根据桌面的布置来调整位置。这种小盒子专门有 4 种颜色的把手，让原木色的文具变得活泼了一些。而只有一个圆圈和一个弯折的木块的卷笔刀想必不少人就想收入囊中吧。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160827004231AVa9l8DFTxuGqk4b.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160827004231hUQ9Vp16Byb2n5is.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160827004231bt4Ms8lXPNnCkwjy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160827004232M0BWIiDFGhl3zuJT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160827004254M36nxI5KjBAEdyXG.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.660221\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><p>          </p><h3>carved bowl&nbsp;by kutarq studio</h3><p>这个圆形木盒看起来有些平平无奇，却让人忍不住仔细看。它的表面经过了特殊的切割，变成了大小不一的波浪纹，让人想放上一些水晶球。从不同的角度看纹路又像是起伏的山峦，很有层次，能够注意到其中细腻的木纹。它很适合放一些首饰或文具小件，摆在桌面上也是一个很美的展示台。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160827004803U7gBNv8aGIZ3RsTr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160827004803Lhfij6JRDH7n9VXu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160827004803ThjR4uoLxkpyOrdB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160827004802OrjHtfoXJNV3c8WT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.803419\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160827004803MBhaOtF4H0ZkpejI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p>          </p><h3>One Piece by yuue</h3><p>这款桌面收纳非常讨巧，刻上了圆孔、长方条等凹槽，可以放手机、笔、名片等需要随时拿取的东西。它留出了可见的一部分，有帮助分类的功能，也保持了整洁的观感。明亮的颜色和多种搭配掩盖了榉木材料本身的普通，变清新时尚，也降低了生产成本。设计者是在柏林的中国组合，它被丹麦品牌 Normann Copenhagen 看中购买设计版权，今年年底可上市。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608270048570iLOXachfzHDE6p3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608270048577loTQNAhdKFw8Mi1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160827004858rdV2AJRBbvKOY3HG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160827004858n91eEw4TU2sVQjDg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}